headline: Booking Holdings to Webcast Second Quarter 2025 Financial Results on July 29
summary: Booking Holdings (NASDAQ: BKNG) announced today that it intends to hold a conference call to discuss its second quarter 2025 financial results on Tuesday, July 29 at 4:30 p.m. ET. The event will be webcast at ir.bookingholdings.com and the audio will be available for replay on the website for seven days thereafter.
